            <Section1 ID="Sec00364" Type="Conclusion">
              <Heading>Conclusion</Heading>
              <Para>The EFA improves the statistical performance for both pollutants. It also slightly improves the threshold exceedance detection. Both ensemble methods make less hits than the model itself, but produce significantly less false alarms.</Para>
              <Para>The advantage of the EFA lies in its ability to compute space-dependent weights, which allows to better account for the small patterns found in the analyses. It is noteworthy that the EFA reproduces well the analyses and is therefore highly dependent on the quality of these analyses.</Para>
              <Para>Further works will consist in developing an online data assimilation method based on the BLUE method and to improve the ensemble detection skills.</Para>
            </Section1>
